# LogTrendWatcher - Log Pattern Analysis Tool

LogTrendWatcher reveals frequently repeated messages, keyword trends, and possible attack indicators.

## Features
- Frequency and time-based summaries  
- Keyword alerts  
- Supports big log files  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/main_LogTrendWatcher.git
cd main_LogTrendWatcher
python analyze.py
